                  <summary change="#ai-catalogue">
                     <p>رساله ادبيه</p>
                     <p>A Persian treatise on the education of children by Áqá-yi-Mutarjim Ibn
                        <lb/>Muḥammad Mahdí-yi-Tabrizi, who transcribed it at Qum in 1295/1878.</p>
                     <p>Begins:</p>
                     <p>الحمد لله ربّ العالمين ... امّا بعد چون خدمت بر دولت و ملت فریضهٔ دمت و
                        لازمه انسانیت</p>
                     <p>و مدنیت است</p>
                     <p>Pp. 101 of 21,5 x 16,5 c. and 11 ll. Fair nim-shikasta. From the library of
                        <lb/>Mr C. Lyne.</p>
                  </summary>
